  <h1 id="pipeline-tool">Pipeline Tool</h1>
  
<p>The MonoGame Pipeline Tool (Pipeline.exe) is the front-end GUI editor for MonoGame content builder projects.</p>
<p align="center">
<img src="images/pipeline.png" alt="Pipeline Tool">
</p>

<p>The Pipeline Tool has the following features:</p>
<ul>
<li>Create, open, and save MGCB projects.</li>
<li>Import existing XNA .contentproj.</li>
<li>Tree view showing content of project.</li>
<li>Property grid for editing content settings.</li>
<li>Full undo/redo support.</li>
<li>Build, rebuild, and clean the project.</li>
<li>Rebuild selected items.</li>
<li>Create new content like fonts and xml.</li>
<li>Support for custom importers/processors/writers.</li>
<li>Template format for adding new custom content types.</li>
</ul>
<p>The Pipeline Tool is included in the SDK installation.</p>
<p><a href="../content/using_pipeline_tool.html">Read detailed documentation</a></p>

